claim.claim-text:
13. An order assembly production method comprising the steps of: 
showing an order-entry screen to select a frame of a product to be manufactured and an essential unit; 
generating a main body model number based on items selected on the order-entry screen; 
creating a manufacturing parts list for each main body model number based on a product components list showing a list of units as the selectable essential units of each model and the items selected on the order-entry screen; and 
settling delivery time based on a production schedule formed every model and the manufacturing parts list of each main body model number and instructing to start production.
